{"word":"H6963 - קֹול - qôwl - kole - Aloud","slug":"H6963","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קֹול</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qôwl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kole"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Aloud"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E7;&#x05D5;&#x05DC; - qo&#x0302;l  qo&#x0302;l</b> - <i>kole, kole</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>call</i> aloud; a <i>voice</i> or <i>sound: - </i> + aloud, bleating, crackling, cry (+ out), fame, lightness, lowing, noise, + hold peace, [pro-] claim, proclamation, + sing, sound, + spark, thunder (-ing), voice, + yell."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7022\">H7022</a>, <a href=\"#/H7031\">H7031</a>, <a href=\"#/H7040\">H7040</a>, <a href=\"#/H7043\">H7043</a>, <a href=\"#/H7044\">H7044</a>, <a href=\"#/H7045\">H7045</a>, <a href=\"#/H7052\">H7052</a>"}]}